  "comments": {
    "overrides": "jwks-rsa (via firebase-admin) does require('jose'); jose v5+ is ESM-only and breaks require() in the serverless build. Pin jose to the last CJS release (v4). jwks-rsa only uses importJWK/exportSPKI, which exist in v4."
